cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SD, cs.HC 

This paper is about building a dialogue agent to fulfill complex tasks, which involves natural language processing and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also proposes a hierarchical deep reinforcement learning approach, which falls under the categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper involves experiments with simulated and real users, which relates to the sub-categories of cs.SD (Software Engineering) and cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction).
